						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1620 and Kali 4699 = 1698 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records some deed of charity given to Narasiṅgagōvinda-baṭṭar of Vāttullāsa gōtra by the trustees of the Mīnāṭchi Sundarēchurar temple along with the ūravar, the royal officer Kamparayyaṉār, and others assigning some land in Kōdachēri. The donee had to give a part of the produce of the land to the temple for worship. </p>						

						</summary>
